{"tid":1507993,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家好 我係用Twitter文宣既一員 對假文宣既事有d野想講","createTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:28:55.000Z","uid":184581,"like":125,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcf002369c455a53e34f09826ef0c86c8603df9","tid":1507993,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:20:58.000Z","msg":"Twitter主要係外國文宣 我希望唔好有假文宣<br />\n原因:<br />\n1.全世界都屌緊中共出fake news同打擊fake news 因為呢種抹黑既行為外國好敏感<br />\n<br />\n2.twitter有好多5毛 同中立記者佢地會不斷澄清同放大我地做既fake news 所以文宣唔到人 仲可能比人屌翻轉頭<br />\n<br />\n3.我地有好多未用既文宣係手冇必要做假文宣<br />\n<br />\n4.之前警察開真槍單野 因為我地冇放佢地比人打既片 只係得佢拔槍踢人 有好多人話我地仲fake news 再睇下比人打果條片既觀看次數就知冇得做假 有唔少幾萬 幾10萬follow既人都因為放左尾 冇放 頭要馬上放翻前一分鐘既片澄清<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我認為我地冇必要做fake news比外國人<br />\n就算做左都fake唔到外國人 因為佢地真係9成都好醒</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd7455e1d3e15f3e09760a2dceab42ca1f80cf26","tid":1507993,"uid":35842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=53d4c3b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/2398098013607797?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1170684516349159%2Fposts%2F