tter文宣<br />\n好多外國人唔知<br />\n宣傳完721就可以宣傳葉虎"},{"pid":"e409c21be0053b161c0bc8ce9e9af180dcb6b568","tid":1507993,"uid":53233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b12cd02c2d985d64b740c3dc154f2cbc4b22f6","tid":1507993,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a505a0ccf165c028589fd1e227ec9c0f9a162f48","tid":1507993,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"要考慮下邊一類嘅fake news<br />\n如果你地係作老屈差佬or政府嘅就對藍屍陣營冇影響<br />\n自己人唔需要呢d野 仲會影響埋己方嘅公信力 三思而行<br />\n如果係建基於藍屍陣營fake news 再同佢作d更誇張嘅野落去confuse佢地<br />\n或者仲可以考慮下實際點樣做 同埋點樣唔影響自己人<br />\n參考此post:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1507383/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1507383/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef8353d327ceda9fb216a42549b118db8020bdb","tid":1507993,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd27107a7c4dd59dfb244e1df11fc4c00df21b15","tid":1507993,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68e48078e4613f4c16649ae19260017a646432ee","tid":1507993,"uid":291526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"文宣巴絲實知道<br />\n真&zwnj;&zwnj;NEWS都推唔切，點解要推FAKE NEWS<br />\n咁多時間不如做好中英雙語，甚至更多語種嘅文宣啦<br />\n一旦FAKE NEWS被廣泛流傳，然後被打假<br />\n咁其他真NEWS都冇晒公信力！"},{"pid":"55a9728d272ec18c1d151b80de083147dd634462","tid":1507993,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76c605cbaae38ac05c9108b8c21309510eb19756","tid":1507993,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re